              "title": "Prometheus",
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "### Prometheus\n“In Greek mythology, Prometheus (/prəˈmiːθiːəs/; Greek: Προμηθεύς, pronounced [promɛːtʰéu̯s], possibly meaning \"forethought\")[1] is a Titan, culture hero, and trickster figure who is credited with the creation of man from clay, and who defies the gods by stealing fire and giving it to humanity….” https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Prometheus\n\nIn the world of Cloud DevOps, Prometheus is a very useful, flexible tool for our monitoring.",
              "instructor_notes": ""
            },
