              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "### Install and Configure Node Exporter\nNext we want to install a node exporter as a new user, and configure it to send data into Promotheus. A detailed [tutorial to install a node_exporter](https://prometheus.io/docs/guides/node-exporter/) is available here. ",
